{"tid":2169945,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府改口 全港設逾百採樣中心  票站投票唔得 排隊檢測又得","createTime":"2020-08-23T01:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T03:44:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e1bc219bc40d3ea55aad65e2d882e9af53b2a5","tid":2169945,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T01:54:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200823/RTOTFK4AYVDRVKJNYGASNH6H2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200823%2FRTOTFK4AYVDRVKJNYGASNH6H2M%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6dXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=8f993965\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200823%2FRTOTFK4AYVDRVKJNYGASNH6H2M%2F&h=a09bfb75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200823/RTOTFK4AYVDRVKJNYGASNH6H2M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n政府改口 全港設逾百採樣中心 <br />\n票站投票唔得 排隊檢測又得<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥上月底以「疫情嚴峻」及「保障公共安全和市民健康」為由，宣佈押後原定下月初舉行的立法會選舉。同一個人、同一個理由、同於下月初，卻決定在全港18區遍設過百採樣中心，安排可能達數以百萬計市民前往接受檢測。多名立法會議員批評「普及社區檢測計劃」與防疫政策矛盾，選舉投票風險遠比檢測小，嘲諷政府「只許州官檢疫，不准百姓投票」，要求如期舉行立法會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：明愛借場先斬後奏 恐致社區爆疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JTl8JHqoYeM_SsZuI2qKQ7WLzes=/1535x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A5LPJRJOZRFDZKX5UIBQCYXIYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJTl8JHqoYeM_SsZuI2qKQ7WLzes%3D%2F1535x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA5LPJRJOZRFDZKX5UIBQCYXIYE.jpg&h=a6446d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳肇始昨指當局正在全港18區物色100處採樣中心，被轟變相製造100個高風險場所。<br />\n<br />\n普及社區檢測計劃將於9月1日展開，為期最多兩星期，專家指出，計劃須有500萬人參與才理想。食衞局長陳肇始。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uPX7SSNDI9xQchJRP3fylCvUM2c=/1122x1530/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X3LRNFK4DZDWXHHOPL3N2DUSFA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuPX7SSNDI9xQchJRP3fylCvUM2c%3D%2F1122x1530%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX3LRNFK4DZDWXHHOPL3N2DUSFA.gif&h=10ec24e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■明愛在無諮詢下，決定將位於香港仔及牛頭角的社區中心借予政府做採樣中心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KZITgA0yXh7U54Z_IaryTdMK-nU=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JTLJUFSWV5EXFKI2NU2ST4EIPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKZITgA0yXh7U54Z_IaryTdMK-nU%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJTLJUFSWV5EXFKI2NU2ST4EIPY.jpg&h=fa61ac03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■近60萬人上月參與民主派舉辦的立會初選，並跟足防疫措施及社交距離排隊，未見導致疫情惡化。<br />\n目標500萬人參與 多過登記選民<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始稱，政府正落區視察場地的空氣通風設備及感染控制措施，並就排隊方法。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：專家料全民檢測假陽性達3%<br />\n<br />\n若最終如願有500萬人參與，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭本月7日召開抗疫記者會時曾說，安排普及社區檢測時會恪守社交距離原則，避免人群聚集及排隊。她當日說：「正因為我哋害怕人群聚集同排隊以至其他風險，我哋先作咗一個艱難決定&mdash;&mdash;延後立法會選舉，所以冇理由因為做普及檢測而又製造好多群組聚集或數以萬計市民喺街上排隊嘅現象。」<br />\n<br />\n因此當日林鄭表明，普及社區檢測計劃會安排市民自行索取及交回樣本瓶，即由市民自行採樣，而不是由醫護人員替市民採樣。但其後多名專家質疑市民自行採樣會減低檢測效果，政府又忘記初心，決定由醫護人員採樣。<br />\n<br />\n議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜批評政府自打嘴巴，令人失笑，「有500至600萬人參加先有代表性，咁多人聚集，冇事都變有事啦」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OQENwAmhX0YFrl6N5mz862ardH8=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VB6QIGKDM5FM7KRMKHIUOQSV7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOQENwAmhX0YFrl6N5mz862ardH8%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVB6QIGKDM5FM7KRMKHIUOQSV7E.jpg&h=10d2122b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地檢測團隊昨乘專車到中山公園體育館的實驗室視察。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒：投票全程戴罩 風險更細<br />\n<br />\n人民力量立法會議員陳志全亦指，林鄭政府以防止人群聚集為由將立會選舉延期，但在二人限聚令仍生效期間推出全民檢測，令不少市民反感，形容是「只許州官檢疫，不准百姓投票」。。。。。。。。。。。批評「根本係政治不作為，唔想搞選舉」。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒說，「選舉播毒風險小過檢測好多，首先投票過程唔會除口罩，初選睇到大家都好守規矩投票」，但全民檢測需市民除口罩進行，且採鼻腔和咽喉兩個樣本，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他續說：「。。。。。。。」"},{"pid":"012bed8c0d53369c0ff892179417fcd44bb72650","tid":2169945,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳"},{"pid":"fb4081594b48c76808c96057f7db9673f3ab0f09","tid":2169945,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea5b5400c4415f130652ee5d8090a0308282615","tid":2169945,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:11:30.000Z","msg":"怕輸比35+囉"},{"pid":"beaec4cac37d96cad0f645f1783657133cdefeb8","tid":2169945,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"病毒知你唔係排隊投票，唔會攪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50011231b5a9c1d950c51199f15340146b0537af","tid":2169945,"uid":311837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"驗到有人中咗係咪去過排隊都要隔離？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}